OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,FThe charity says it is being forced to
OL,7,Freduce its number of inpatient beds
OL,8,Fand cut the equivalent of 45 full-time
OL,9,Froles ` around 14% of its overall
OL,10,Fworkforce.
OL,12,FIt did have 24 inpatient beds ` 12 at
OL,13,FErdington and 12 at Selly Park. Bed
OL,14,Fnumbers will reduce to 16 in total ` 8
OL,15,Fat each hospice site.
