OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,FBirmingham Hospice says it needs to
OL,7,Fraise #6.5 million through fundraising
OL,8,Factivity, income from shops and
OL,9,Fvoluntary donations to cover the costs
OL,10,Fof running the charity which breaks
OL,11,Fdown to #1,678,509 per month or
OL,12,F#55,335 per day.
OL,14,FThey say 42% of costs need to be
OL,15,Fcovered through fundraising activity,
OL,16,Fincome from shops and voluntary
OL,17,Fdonations.
OL,19,FITV News Central has contacted NHS
OL,20,FEngland for comment.
